{"tid":1450343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:32:48.000Z","uid":182506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e0c2418c1c11646ab443344d0f51002342206e","tid":1450343,"uid":182506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=032c6035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fh&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=a63fa571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/h</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"a74f41c581bb511d14cdafc8aea4ceba0a509d88","tid":1450343,"uid":11322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}